}} 'Ends' is a collection of science fiction stories and poems by Gordon R.
Dickson. It was first published by Baen Books in 1988 and as a companion volume
to Dickson's [[Beginnings (collection)|Beginnings]]. Most of the stories
originally appeared in the magazines [[Analog Science Fiction and Fact]],
[[Astounding]], [[if (magazine)|If]], [[Galaxy Science Fiction]], Destinies,
Science Fiction Stories and [[Amazing Stories]] The poems first appeared in The
Final Encyclopedia.
